13 September 2019 On 17 September 2019, GCIS will host the Thusong Service Excellence Awards ceremony in recognition of public servants at Thusong Service Centres who have distinguished themselves in the execution of their duties. The year 2019 marks 20 years since the existence of the Thusong Service Centre Programme which was initiated in 1999 as one of the access strategy aimed at redressing the imbalances of the past by taking services and information closer to the people. Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: 17 September 2019Time: 17h00Venue: Grand West Casino, Cape Town RSPV: Gerzell Mathey at : gerzell@gcis.gov.za or 072 276 3492 Follow the conversation on @GCISMedia @GovernmentZA #ThusongWeek #PublicServiceMonthEnquiries: Phumla WilliamsCell: 083 5010 139